reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater well-made with good quality and thickness, appreciating its chic style and soft, comfortable feel.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Chic
items.body: Love this PRETTYGARDEN fall quarter zip! The dark green color is gorgeous and perfect for the season. It’s soft, fitted, and flattering — great for layering or wearing on its own. Stylish and comfy for everyday wear! Read more
items.author: Claudia Mireya

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Happy with the quality
items.body: I LOVE this top and I may buy it in another color. I usually wear a medium but I ordered a large and it fits just right. The material is soft and comfy. Would buy it again. Read more
items.author: Mark Soucie

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Ribbed Pullover with Retro Zipper Vibe
items.body: First off, I'm 5'8, 133 lbs, and a 36B with a bit of a longer torso and arms. I bought the Large in the wine red shade which is a gorgeous color. This sweater is very soft, a bit form-fitting/clingy. It offers generous stretch while still maintaining a fitted shape. I love the 60s/70s vibe of the round zipper pull and the overall design of the sweater. I did, however, deduct a star because when lifting my arms up, the sweater tended to bunch up and needed to be pulled down frequently (probably due to the clingy nature of the sweater). Maybe an XL would prevent this for me, but then it might fit too big on top. Update: I machine laundered this sweater and hang-dried, hoping that the substantial wet weight of the sweater may help to elongate the torso. Sadly, it did not since the material has a lot of clingy memory so it bounced right back to its original fit. Read more
items.author: Gina

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful sweater, quality and appearance is so gorgeous !
items.body: The media could not be loaded. This sweater is so nice I wish I ordered more. The quarter zip on this sweater is the perfect size, and the wine color is to die for…. PRETTY GARDEN is always consistently good, wonderful quality. For the price you cannot beat it. The size was perfect, it runs true to size It is so soft, and I have washed it on gently with a tumble dry low and there wasn’t any shrinkage Another winner from Pretty Garden! Read more
items.author: Jane

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars I love this sweater!
items.body: This is adorable and I really like the weight of it: not too hot for indoor gatherings, but warm enough under a jacket for cold winter outings. I just ordered two more in other fall colors. I have a feeling this will be my "go-to" with jeans this fall. It reminds me of a similar sweater I wore in high school (50 years ago)! Medium fits me comfortably (5'4"; 145 lbs), although the sleeves are long. They fold over easily at the wrist, though, and are not too thick. Read more
items.author: Yvonne

items.title: 3.0 out of 5 stars So cute - but zipper was poor quality
items.body: Really wanted to keep this, but zipper was poor quality. As for the quality of the actual sweater - fit was spot on for me, and material was nice. Even loved the color, soft shade. Perfect fall sweater. Read more
items.author: CamperD

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great buy
items.body: Best clothing item i have purchased off Amazon. It is soft and fits perfectly Read more
items.author: Heather Faulkner

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great pullover
items.body: Love the pullover, the material is soft, not too thick and it can be dressed up or down. Unfortunately it is just one size too big. I am planning on getting a new one soon. Read more
items.author: Elizabeth

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

For the best look, smooth the fabric, check the neckline placement, and pair it with shoes that match the occasion and the hem length.

Comfort comes from both the cut and the fabric, so selecting your preferred fit makes a noticeable difference over a full day of wear.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Sky Blue, Dark Pink, Dark Grey, Grey Blue, Light Apricot, Apricot, Army Green, Black, Coffee, Brick Red, Dark Green, Navy, Wine Red, Pink. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
